No. 542,

Misc.

Midgett v. Clifford et al. H. Clay Espey for petitioner. Albert J. Ahem, Jr. and Charles W. Halleck for respondents.

Motion to strike appendix “B” to the petition for writ of cer-tiorari denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.
